Spring AOP (Aspect Oriented programming)
----------------------------------------
Spring AOP is a way to handle Cross cutting Concerns without mixing them into our business logic.(EX: Logging)
Instead of repeating Code you define it in one place and appy wherever you needed.

Annotations:
-------------
@EnableAspectJAutoProxy - Enables AOP in our application. ths will be present in config class.
@Aspect - This is class level annotation, The class that holds all the AOP code will be annotated with @Aspect
@Before - If we want to execute a piece of code before a method executes.
@After -  If we want to execute a piece of code After a method executes.
@Around - If we want to execute a piece of code Before a method executes and after the method execution.

